Chef Wanted with Anne Burrell - Season 3, Episode 1




Beachside Bistro

After a multi-million dollar upgrade, the exclusive Bacara Resort & Spa in Santa Barbara, Calif., is searching for a new Executive Chef for their restaurant, The Bistro. Anne Burrell brings four candidates who will be tested on their ability to combine fresh land and sea ingredients into dishes worthy of this world-class resort.





Original Air Date: 01-Aug-2013
